text:
@realDonaldTrump You say a lot of things.

As for me, still waiting for that 10% tax cut you promised to the working class in 2018, immediately prior to the 2018 midterms. 

Also waiting for the #coronavirus to magically disappear.

Did you fix the deficit yet, as promised? https://t.co/cPo190GIyw
